<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>4</hymn_number>
<title>Ʋba Chihowa ma! ƲIT4</title>
<time_sig>S.M. (6.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<aka>Omniscience of God.</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba Chihowa ma!
 Et akahchunolit,
 Chi̱ holhponayo fehna ka,
 Et pi o̱ kahanchí.

[V2]
 Nitak, ninak moma,
 Pi o̱ hopo̱koyot,
 Luak libbi choyuhmi hosh
 Ish pi on tomashke.

[V3]
 Kanimak fehna ho̱
 Nowʋt iloh a̱ya,
 Peh iloh aiasha kia,
 Pi pi̱sa banoshke.

[V4]
 Chihowa pulla hosh
 Hatak e moma ka
 Pithana bieka hoke;
 Iloh i̱ yimmashke.

[V5]
 Pim anukfila hʋt
 I̱ haiaka bano,
 Katioht il in luma wa;
 Iloh ithanashke.</lyrics>
</song>